# JCR paths of the AEM components to migrate. One per line; `#` for comments.
# `aem-to-sanity-schema` reads each `{path}/_cq_dialog.infinity.json` and emits
# a Sanity schema type. Add paths in waves as you migrate; unmapped resource
# types surface in the schema audit (`output/cache/schema-audit.json`) so you
# know what's still pending.
#
# Discover paths by browsing CRXDE at `<AEM_AUTHOR_URL>/crx/de/` under
# `/apps/<your-namespace>/components/`, or hit
# `<AEM_AUTHOR_URL>/apps/<your-namespace>/components.1.json` for a tree view.
#
# Example shape (replace with your own):
# /apps/acme/components/content/hero-banner
# /apps/acme/components/content/promo
# /apps/acme/components/content/feature-list
